      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of Apr 27 obituary and three later articles that misstated date of theatrical producer David Merrick's death</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A front-page obituary of the theatrical producer David Merrick on April 27 and three later articles, including one on July 19 about a memorial tribute at the St. James Theater, misstated the date of his death. It was April 25, not April 26. The David Merrick Arts Foundation reported the error in a fax to The Times on Friday.</p>
      </block>
